node.text:
@franco.urbaez is a self-made millionaire turning heads in the world of Digital Marketing. As CEO and Founder of 𝐃𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐦 𝐁𝐢𝐠 𝐌𝐞𝐝𝐢𝐚, he helps entrepreneurs scale their businesses to 30K-100K a month while helping them find their dream clients using his highly successful organic marketing automation tool, Pepper.⁣
⁣
In 2017 @franco.urbaez quit his $27/hr warehouse job for his chance at personal and financial freedom. It wasn’t until he lost 18K in savings that he realized he needed to invest in a mentor. Living on credit, he took a risk and hired 𝐑𝐮𝐬𝐬𝐞𝐥𝐥 𝐁𝐫𝐮𝐧𝐬𝐨𝐧. ⁣
⁣
Having generated over a million dollars for himself and his clients, the risk paid off. He has earned the prestigious 𝟐 𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐚 𝐂𝐥𝐮𝐛 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝 from Clickfunnels and holds the world record for highest conversion rate at a live event, a MINDBLOWING 95.8%!! ⁣
⁣
@franco.urbaez is now helping other entrepreneurs achieve their freedom and scale their businesses to 7 Figures by providing them with the tools to find the right clients and the knowledge to confidently price their services and close more deals! ⁣
⁣
If you’re ready to take action and start & scale your Marketing Agency to $100K/Month DM @franco.urbaez the words “30K AGENCY”⁣
⁣
Follow 👉🏼 @franco.urbaez and DM him the word “30K AGENCY” to get help! 🔥⁣
Follow 👉🏼 @franco.urbaez⁣
Follow 👉🏼 @franco.urbaez⁣
Follow 👉🏼 @franco.urbaez to take your life and business to the next level!
